ActEconomic Action Plan 2014 Act, No. 2
Economic Action Plan 2015 Act, No. 1
SubjectOrder Fixing November 5, 2018 as the Day on which Certain Provisions of the two Acts Come into Force
PrecisOrder fixing (1) November 5, 2018, as the day on which sections 102 to 113 the the ECONOMIC ACTION PLAN 2014 ACT, NO.2, chapter 39 of the Statutes of Canada 2014, COMES INTO FORCE; and, (2) November 5, 2018, as the day on which sections 44 to 49 of the ECONOMIC ACTION PLAN 2015, NO. 1, chapter 36 of the Statutes of Canada 2015, COMES INTO FORCE.
